Wend joma owar


1  

Eka ne ang’icho, mi aneno Nyarombo kochung’ e got Sayun. Ne en gi ji alufu mia achiel gi piero ang’wen gang’wen, (
144  ,
000  ) kendo nyinge owuon gi nying Wuon mare nondiki e lela wang’ jogo. 
2  Ne awinjo dwol moro moa e polo kawuo ka pi mang’eny, kendo machalo gi polo mamor matek. Chutho, dwol mane awinjono ne chalo mana gi dwond joma goyo thum. 
3  Ne giwero wer manyien e nyim kom duong’ kendo e nyim gik mangima ang’wen kod jodongo kande. To onge ng’ama ne nyalo puonjore wendno mak mana ji alufu mia achiel gi mia ang’wen gang’wen, (
144  ,
000  ) ma gin kende e joma ne owar oa e piny. 
4  Magi e joma ne ok odwanyore gi mon, to ne giritore maler. Giluwo Nyarombo kamoro amora modhiye. Osewargi kuom ji mana kaka olemo mokwongo nyak, michiwo ni Nyasaye kendo ni Nyarombo. 
5  

Miriambo ne ok owuok e dhogi, kendo gionge gi ketho moro kata achiel.

Malaika adek


6  Eka ne aneno malaika moro ka huyo e kor polo. Ne en gi Wach Maber mochwere mondo oland ni joma odak e piny. Nolando wachno ni pinje duto, kod ogendini duto. 
7  Nokok matek niya, “Luoruru Nyasaye, kendo miyeuru duong’, nikech sa mong’adoe bura osechopo! Lamuru Jal mane ochueyo polo gi piny kaachiel gi nam kod sokni.”


8  

Eka malaika mar ariyo noluwe kawacho niya, “Yaya Babulon, dala maduong’, osepodho! Osepodho! En e dhako mane omiyo ogendini duto omadho divai mar terruokne. En divai makelo mirimb Nyasaye.”


9  Bang’ mano, malaika mar adek nobiro bang’gi kawacho matek niya, “Ng’ato ang’ata malamo ondiek kod gima ket kode, mi oyudo alama e lela wang’e kata e lwete, 
10  

nyaka madh divai mar mirimb Nyasaye moruw makech e kikombe mar mirimbe. Noyud sand mar mach makakni e nyim malaika maler, kendo e nyim Nyarombo. 
11  

To iro mar mach masandogi nodum malo nyaka chieng’. Bende jogo malamo Ondiek kod gima ket kode, kata moyudo alama mar nyinge, ok noyud yueyo odiechieng’ gotieno.” 
12  Ka eri ema idwaroe kinda mar jo-Nyasaye, kendo ma ok we yie ma gin-go kuom Yesu!


13  Eka ne awinjo dwol moa e polo kawacho niya, “Ndik ni, ‘Chakre kawuono, jogo matho kogeno kuom Ruoth, gin johawi!’ ” Roho bende wacho ni, “Ee, gin johawi adier, nikech giniyue kuom tichgi matek, nimar gik ma gisetimo dhi kodgi.”

Keyo mar piny


14  

Eka ne ang’icho mi aneno bor polo marachar, to ewi bor polono ne nitie gima obetie machalo gi dhano. Ne osidho osimbo mar dhahabu e wiye, kendo ne oting’o pala mar keyo mabith e lwete. 
15  

Eka malaika machielo nowuok e Hekalu kakok matek ni jal mane obet e bor polono niya, “Kaw pandi mar keyo mondo ike nikech kinde mar keyo osechopo, kendo piny ochiek mokadho!” 
16  Omiyo jal mane obet e bor polo notiyo gi pande mar keyo e piny mi okayo piny.


17  Bang’ mano, malaika moro nowuok e Hekalu manie polo. En bende ne en gi pand keyo mabith. 
18  Eka malaika machielo man gi teko kuom mach noa e kendo-mar-misango. Ne okok matek ni malaika mane nigi pand keyo mabithno niya, “Kaw pandi mar keyo mabithno mondo ichok olemb mzabibu mag piny nikech olembene ochiek ahinya!” 
19  Omiyo, malaikano notiyo gi pande mar keyo e piny, mi ochoko olemb mzabibu mag piny, mobologi kar biyo mzabibu maduong’ mar mirimb Nyasaye. 
20  

Olembe ne obi kinyono kar bichono e alap mar dala, kendo remo mamol kawuok kar bichono, mochopo kilomita adek koa e dala, to tut remono ne dirom mita ariyo.

